@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@json = application/json

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### PREREQUIS
### 1) Run login requests first in REST Client so cookies are persisted.
### 2) Replace placeholder IDs below after create/list calls.
### -----------------------------------------------------------------

@offreId = REPLACE_OFFRE_ID
@candidatureId = REPLACE_CANDIDATURE_ID

### A1) Register tenant + admin (public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/entreprise/registerEntreprise
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "nom": "Talentia QA",
  "email": "entreprise.qa@example.com",
  "adresse": "Tunis",
  "secteur": "Tech",
  "plan": "pro",
  "adminName": "Admin QA",
  "adminEmail": "admin.qa@example.com",
  "adminPassword": "Admin123!"
}

### A2) Login admin (saves jwt cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/user/login
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "email": "admin.qa@example.com",
  "password": "Admin123!"
}

### A3) Create offer (admin cookie required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/offre/createOffre
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "post": "Developpeur Node",
  "description": "Backend ATS",
  "requirements": ["Node.js", "MongoDB"],
  "typeContrat": "CDI",
  "localisation": "Tunis",
  "modeContrat": "hybride",
  "departement": "IT",
  "niveauExperience": "mid"
}

### A4) Register candidate (public)
POST {{baseUrl}}/candidat/inscrire
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "nom": "Candidat QA",
  "email": "candidat.qa@example.com",
  "motDePasse": "Candidat123!",
  "telephone": "99999999"
}

### A5) Login candidate (saves jwt_candidat cookie)
POST {{baseUrl}}/candidat/connecter
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "email": "candidat.qa@example.com",
  "motDePasse": "Candidat123!"
}

### A6) Set candidate profile CV (candidate cookie required)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/candidat/mettreAJourProfil
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "cv_url": "cv_candidate_qa.pdf",
  "linkedin": "https://linkedin.com/in/candidat-qa",
  "salaireAttendu": 3000,
  "disponibilite": "Immediate"
}

### A7) Candidate applies (candidate cookie required)
POST {{baseUrl}}/candidature/postuler
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "offre": "{{offreId}}",
  "lettre_motivation": "Je suis motive pour ce poste"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### PROBLEME 1 - Pipeline data must include candidature cv_url + candidat fields
### Check in response data[*]:
### - cv_url at candidature level
### - candidat.telephone, candidat.salaireAttendu, candidat.disponibilite, candidat.linkedin
### -----------------------------------------------------------------
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidature/getAllCandidatures?offre={{offreId}}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### PROBLEME 4 - Transition preselectionne -> entretien_passe must be allowed
### -----------------------------------------------------------------

### B1) Move to preselectionne
PUT {{baseUrl}}/candidature/updateCandidatureEtape/{{candidatureId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "etape": "preselectionne"
}

### B2) Move directly to entretien_passe (must return 200)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/candidature/updateCandidatureEtape/{{candidatureId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "etape": "entretien_passe"
}

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### PROBLEME 3 - Refusal should delete planned interviews in backend
### -----------------------------------------------------------------

### C1) Move to entretien_planifie (creates entretien)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/candidature/updateCandidatureEtape/{{candidatureId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{
  "etape": "entretien_planifie",
  "dateEntretien": "2026-04-15T09:30:00.000Z",
  "typeEntretien": "Visio"
}

### C2) Refuse candidature (must also remove related entretiens)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/candidature/refuserCandidature/{{candidatureId}}
Content-Type: {{json}}

{}

### C3) List interviews and verify there is no interview with candidature == {{candidatureId}}
GET {{baseUrl}}/entretien/getAllEntretiens

### -----------------------------------------------------------------
### PROBLEME 2 - Deleting offer should cascade delete candidatures + relations
### -----------------------------------------------------------------

### D1) Delete offer (must include deletedRelations counters)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/offre/deleteOffreById/{{offreId}}

### D2) Verify candidatures by offer is empty or offer not found after deletion
GET {{baseUrl}}/candidature/getCandidaturesByOffre/{{offreId}}
